				<xs:complexType>
					<xs:sequence>
						<xs:element name="PriceType">
							<xs:annotation>
								<xs:documentation xml:lang="en">Select the price type you would like to communicate (SWING, MATURITY, MARKET, HOLD TO MATURITY, ADJUSTED GROSS, ADJUSTED NET)</xs:documentation>
								<xs:documentation xml:lang="de">Preistyp auswählen (SWING, MATURITY, MARKET, HOLD TO MATURITY, ADJUSTED GROSS, ADJUSTED NET)</xs:documentation>
								<xs:documentation xml:lang="fr">Sélectionnez le type de prix que vous souhaitez communiquer (SWING, MATURITY, MARKET, HOLD TO MATURITY, ADJUSTED GROSS, ADJUSTED NET)</xs:documentation>
								<xs:documentation xml:lang="nl">Selecteer het prijstype dat u wilt communiceren (SWING, MATURITY, MARKET, HOLD TO MATURITY, ADJUSTED GROSS, ADJUSTED NET)</xs:documentation>
								<xs:documentation xml:lang="es">Seleccione el tipo de precio que desea comunicar (SWING, MATURITY, MARKET, HOLD TO MATURITY, ADJUSTED GROSS, ADJUSTED NET)</xs:documentation>
								<xs:documentation xml:lang="it">Seleziona la tipologia di prezzo che vuoi comunicare (SWING, SCADENZA, MERCATO, TENERE A SCADENZA, LORDO RETTIFICO, NETTO RETTIFICATO)</xs:documentation>
								<xs:documentation xml:lang="cs">Vyberte typ ceny, který chcete komunikovat (SWING, MATURITY, MARKET, HOLD TO MATURITY, ADJUSTED GROSS, ADJUSTED NET)</xs:documentation>
								<xs:documentation xml:lang="hu">Válassza ki a kommunikálni kívánt ártípust (SWING, MATURITY, MARKET, HOLD TO MATURITY, ADJUSTED GROSS, ADJUSTED NET)</xs:documentation>
